text.tspan: If a person says hi to Xin but does not say his name. Could make them as forgot Xin. But if a person says hi to Xin but does not say his name but does say hi with someone else's
name next to Xin it's called name hater. This is extremely effective with house news
People that says hi to Xin but does not say his name marks them as forgot Xin. There is a certain code that Xin does if a person does not know his name.
People that Waves hi but not say hi or say hi with his name. Calls as not knowing Xin.
People that does not respond after Xin greet it's called forgotten Xin.
People that does say hi and with his name reset the forgot Xin meter on them.
People that says hi and says his name first before Xin Greets them also reset the forgot Xin meter on them.
People that ignores Xin greet causes them as a Shy and not trustworthy person
